    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to roll! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it starts up and moves under its own power, giving you a solid foundation to work with. You'll notice significant wear inside and out, and it will need some mechanical attention and cosmetic work to get it back to its best. Perfect for the hands-on buyer, a parts project, or someone looking for the most affordable entry point into car ownership!",
