      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is a rare find in today's market \u2014 a true mint-condition example that has been meticulously maintained from day one. Boasting flawless paintwork, an immaculate interior free of wear or blemish, and a mechanically sound drivetrain that performs exactly as intended, this car drives as confidently as it looks. Full service records available upon request. Whether you're a discerning enthusiast or simply demand the very best, this is a vehicle you can buy with complete confidence. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special.",
      "price": 46000.0,
